title: Bobby Has Freak Out Moment During Rock Climbing Date + How Was Your Proposal Ruined? + Bobby On How Make Up Testers Are Making You Sick!

description:
Bobby went on a rock climbing date over the weekend and had a freak out moment after getting a flashback from his episode of Running Wild with Bear Grylls. Bobby talks about a proposal where a guy lost the wedding ring in the ocean…and then takes calls on how listeners proposals were ruined. Plus, how make up testers can make you really sick!
